  "prompt": "What are movies that everyone should see?",
  "response": "Determining which movies everyone should see is subjective and can vary greatly based on personal tastes and cultural context. However, here are some suggestions that span different genres and eras, and are widely regarded as classics or influential films:\n\n1. **Drama:**\n   - \"The Shawshank Redemption\" (1994)\n   - \"Forrest Gump\" (1994)\n   - \"Schindler\u2019s List\" (1993)\n\n2. **Action/Adventure:**\n   - \"Die Hard\" (1988)\n   - \"Mad Max: Fury Road\" (2015)\n   - \"Indiana Jones: Raiders of the Lost Ark\" (1981)\n\n3. **Science Fiction:**\n   - \"Star Wars: Episode IV - A New Hope\" (1977)\n   - \"Blade Runner\" (1982)\n   - \"The Matrix\" (1999)\n\n4. **Fantasy:**\n   - \"The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring\" (2001)\n   - \"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone\" (2001)\n   - \"Pan's Labyrinth\" (2006)\n\n5. **Comedy:**\n   - \"Groundhog Day\" (1993)\n   - \"Monty Python and the Holy Grail\" (1975)\n   - \"The Grand Budapest Hotel\" (2014)\n\n6. **Horror:**\n   - \"Psycho\" (1960)\n   - \"The Exorcist\" (1973)\n   - \"Get Out\" (2017)\n\n7. **Romance:**\n   - \"Casablanca\" (1942)\n   - \"Titanic\" (1997)\n   - \"Pride and Prejudice\" (2005)\n\n8. **Animated:**\n   - \"Toy Story\" (1995)\n   - \"Spirited Away\" (2001)\n   - \"The Lion King\" (1994)\n\n9. **Musicals:**\n   - \"The Sound of Music\" (1965)\n   - \"West Side Story\" (1961)\n   - \"La La Land\" (2016)\n\n10. **Classics:**\n    - \"Citizen Kane\" (1941)\n    - \"Gone with the Wind\" (1939)\n    - \"One Flew Over the Cuckoo\u2019s Nest\" (1975)\n\nThese films represent a mixture of critical acclaim, cultural significance, and widespread popularity. Watching them not only provides entertainment but also offers insight into different filmmaking styles, eras, and societal perspectives.",
